  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Use the concepts of vibrational and rotational energy to describe energy transitions in a diatomic molecule</item>
<item>Explain key features of a vibrational-rotational energy spectrum of a diatomic molecule</item>
<item>Estimate allowed energies of a rotating molecule</item>
<item>Determine the equilibrium separation distance between atoms in a diatomic molecule from the vibrational-rotational absorption spectrum</item></list></md:abstract>
